Comment: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:57.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}崩れて終わる世界
Comment: 0,0:00:57.49,0:01:06.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}無慈悲に告げる
Comment: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:13.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}君は  一人
Comment: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:19.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}何を  聞いてた
Comment: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:25.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}僕は  遠い
Comment: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:32.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}夢を  見てた
Comment: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:34.24,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}何を選び取る
Comment: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:35.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}何を諦める
Comment: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}決めようとしてる
Comment: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}僕は何様だ
Comment: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:40.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}何を選ぶかは
Comment: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:42.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}もう決まっている
Comment: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:43.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}間違いは無いか
Comment: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:45.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}神に問いかける
Comment: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:48.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}一人きりじゃなかった
Comment: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:50.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}ずっとそばにいたんだ
Comment: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:57.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}この手を伸ばす
Comment: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:00.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}怖いものなんかない
Comment: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:04.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}たとえ化け物になろうとも
Comment: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:12.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}成し遂げる
Comment: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:57.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}崩坏的终焉之世
Comment: 0,0:00:57.49,0:01:06.46,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}无情告知
Comment: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:13.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}你默默一人
Comment: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:19.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}在聆听什么
Comment: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:25.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}而我恍惚
Comment: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:32.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}如在远梦中彷徨
Comment: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:34.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}选择什么
Comment: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:35.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}放弃什么
Comment: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}我有何权力
Comment: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}做这些决定
Comment: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:40.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}如何选择
Comment: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:42.29,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}已经确定
Comment: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:43.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}有否错误
Comment: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:45.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}向神询问
Comment: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:48.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}你不是一个人
Comment: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:50.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}一直在你身边
Comment: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:57.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}将这双手伸出
Comment: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:00.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}无所畏惧
Comment: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:04.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}就算是化身怪物
Comment: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:12.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}定将完成夙愿
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——CQ——
